#KampalaRelease
---++ TWiki Release 6.1 (Kampala) released on 2018-07-16

__New Features and Enhancements of TWiki Release 6.1__

%INCLUDE{ "TWikiReleaseNotes06x01" section="featurehighlights" }%

   * *Bug Fixes*
      * 59 bugs fixed in TWiki-6.1.0

See the full list of new features and bug fixes in TWikiReleaseNotes06x01.

#KampalaHallOfFame
