#JerusalemRelease
---++ TWiki Release 6.0 (Jerusalem) released on 2013-10-14 &mdash; 2015-11-29

__New Features and Enhancements of TWiki Release 6.0__

%INCLUDE{ "TWikiReleaseNotes06x00" section="featurehighlights" }%

   * *Bug Fixes*
      * 99 bugs fixed in TWiki-6.0.0
      * 66 bugs fixed in TWiki-6.0.1
      * 53 bugs fixed in TWiki-6.0.2

See the full list of new features and bug fixes in TWikiReleaseNotes06x00.

#JerusalemHallOfFame
