| Install: New testenv function to change the locks in the TWiki database to the web server user id (automates installation step). [[http://TWiki.org/cgi-bin/view/Codev/RelockingRCSFiles][Details]] | TWiki:Main.MattWilkie TWiki:Main.SvenDowideit |
| Install: The shipped .htaccess.txt now needs to be edited before it is valid, to help reduce chances of error. [[http://TWiki.org/cgi-bin/view/Codev/InconsistentExtractDirectory][Details]] | TWiki:Main.CrawfordCurrie TWiki:Main.SvenDowideit |
