%META:TOPICINFO{author="MikeMannix" date="999489686" format="1.0" version="1.41"}%
---+ TWiki History: The Dev Timeline
d8 8
a15 4
	* __JohnTalintyre &#149; 30 Aug 2001 (Mar/May 2001) &#149; Ability to move attachments between topics, see FileAttachments__ MM 
	* __PeterThoeny &#149; 21 Aug 2001 &#149; Convert to XHTML 1.0 goal is to XHTML-ify TWiki. ConvertToXHTML10__ MM 
	* __JohnTalintyre &#149; 26 Jun 2001 &#149; Category information to form using MetaDataDefinition format__ MM 
	* PeterThoeny &#149; 07 Jun 2001 &#149; New topic templates are now topics instead of templates, e.g. can be customized by editing a topic. Retired =notedited.tmpl=, =notext.tmpl= and =notwiki.tmpl= templates. More in TWikiTemplates. 
